    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "あー、つっかれた……\nライブ前の打ち合わせで、こんなに遅くなるなんて",
      "startTime": 5.1666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "franさん、ステージのセットからライティングまで\n随分、意見出してましたもんね",
      "startTime": 11.8666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、せっかくのクリスマスですし\n目一杯華やかにしなきゃ、つまらないじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 16.9000002225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマス、あまりお好きではないのでは？",
      "startTime": 20.266665109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "好きかって言うと、別にそうでもないですけど\n繁華街とか、うるさいですし",
      "startTime": 27.4333317757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "でもイルミネーションとか、店頭のディスプレイとか\nキラキラ光ってるものを見るのは、割と好きですね",
      "startTime": 33.2666640918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "子供の頃、ドイツの親戚の所に\nちょうどクリスマスの時期に行きまして",
      "startTime": 39.7666658719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスマーケットに連れて行ってもらったんですが\nライトアップされた風景が、凄く綺麗だったんです",
      "startTime": 45.4999992053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "……あら？",
      "startTime": 49.1333305041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "あそこの女の人、階段の下でずっと動かないんですけど\n……何かあったのかしら",
      "startTime": 56.1999971707,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3300.003083699998,
          "startTime": 59.5000002544
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "お困りみたいですけど、どうされましたか？\n……ああ、ベビーカーで階段上がるの大変ですよね",
      "startTime": 65.8999943732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "お手伝いしますよ\nああ、気にしないで下さい",
      "startTime": 72.1333277065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "こういう時は、お互い様ですから\n赤ちゃん、今だけ抱いててもらっていいですか？",
      "startTime": 77.6000020026,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7266.664664100006,
          "startTime": 84.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺も手伝いますよ\nfranさんはそっちの荷物を持って下さい……よっと",
      "startTime": 82.7666747728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "ふう……ここまで上がれば大丈夫かしら\n……いえいえ、気にしないで下さい。それでは",
      "startTime": 95.33333381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん。私ってば今、凄く善い行いをしましたよね\n徳もこれで一気に貯まったんじゃないかしら",
      "startTime": 107.3666773156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん\nさっきから変な顔してますけど、何か？",
      "startTime": 114.6000065799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ。本当に、他人に親切にしてるんだなと……",
      "startTime": 118.1333399132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "あら、酷い\nそんなに私が不親切な人間だと思ってたんですか？",
      "startTime": 125.2000035281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いやぁ、そんなことはありませんよ！？",
      "startTime": 129.2000035281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "franさんが事務所のトイレを掃除してくれたと\nこの間も、橋本さんが凄い感謝してましたよ",
      "startTime": 134.6333195682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "あー、事務所をマメに整頓してるのって\n橋本さんか、たまに沙季を見かけるくらいですしね",
      "startTime": 141.4333246544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "kanaは、掃除なんて絶対にやらないですし",
      "startTime": 145.7666579878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasvenue-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "お陰で、私のやることが多くて大変でした\nま、それだけ徳を積めたから良しとしますけど？",
      "startTime": 153.3333246544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（mihoさんが「franがいきなり楽屋を片付ける）\n（ようになって不気味」と言ってたのは、黙っておこう）",
      "startTime": 159.8999913211,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5566.6643781,
          "startTime": 165.4666556992
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん、ふふーん、ふーん……",
      "startTime": 166.9999994591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "随分楽しそうですけど\n何か、いいことでもありましたか？",
      "startTime": 172.0666620568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん\nそうそう、聞いて下さいよ",
      "startTime": 176.6333358443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_02-kor021.m4a",
      "text": "だいぶ前に、お菓子の懸賞に応募してたんですけど\n昨日、家に帰ったら景品が届いてたんです",
      "startTime": 182.0666478153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
